channel.title: Looking for a couple of people to skill & make money with
channel.description:
I haven't played Runescape very much over the last couple years and since the trade is back i am giving it another shot, would anyone care to skill or get together and make some money?
My RSN is Jeljj

item.title: Looking for a couple of people to skill & make money with
item.dc:creator: @mr_extremez mr extremez
item.description:
@mr_extremez wrote:

[quote=“Aetoc, post:13, topic:407512”][quote author=mr extremez link=topic=508801.msg3692988#msg3692988 date=1312242645]

Its not worth it to get back. Its only “fun” to bot and pk.

Botting is boring play the game for real to many people bot now…

I used to play the game. Now the game is filled with idiotic ways to obtain cash and bots in every training spot, the training is too easy even without bots.

Then train for real if its so easy lol.

Why would I spend MY time, when I could bot, with 3/4 the efficiency

Because the games more fun when you play real then just have a bot do things for you im sure at one time you didnt bot…
[/quote]

Well the first time i botted it was so much fun finding out i didn’t have to do one click and watching my stats level up, but now i’m like you and feel the same way.[/quote]
Thank you.
